<p><b>How to get free AR points?</b> When students or parents look up their book in either point scan, arbookfind.com, or TumbleBooks, they should record the author, title, level, and AR quiz number. The student will take a comprehension test on that book at their school to earn AR points. Many schools reward children for earning AR points.</p>
